data.name: Label2.Text
data.value:
When dealing with cryptocurrency you need to download a blockchain.
Before a blockchain is fully downloaded and you are synced to the rest of the network you will not be able to perform anything in your wallet.
Syncing a blockchain from scratch against other peers in the network can take as long as several days.
To speed things up you can download a database export of the chain from one of our repositories. This will most likley still take several hours but will be mutch faster.
